      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782572273005,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "• Elegance verdict: 'mixed' — clean spine (SQL layer, secret handling, L3 bus design) wrapped in dead/mis-wired periphery (registration drift + consolidatable duplication). Dominant pattern: prune-and-rewire on a sound core.\n• Three highest-leverage single fixes: (1) Agent→Task matcher flip revives 12 dead hooks at once (D2b-01); (2) canonical getSessionId unblocks 60.7% corr-null telemetry (D7d-01); (3) shared storeLearning() helper closes S0 junk-creator + poison-inject seam (D5a-01+D5b-01).\n• WS-2 Substrate node represents three components at different health levels — see 'subsystems' diagram for per-component breakdown.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Elegance verdict: 'mixed' — clean spine (SQL layer, secret handling, L3 bus design) wrapped in dead/mis-wired periphery (registration drift + consolidatable duplication). Dominant pattern: prune-and-rewire on a sound core.\n• Three highest-leverage single fixes: (1) Agent→Task matcher flip revives 12 dead hooks at once (D2b-01); (2) canonical getSessionId unblocks 60.7% corr-null telemetry (D7d-01); (3) shared storeLearning() helper closes S0 junk-creator + poison-inject seam (D5a-01+D5b-01).\n• WS-2 Substrate node represents three components at different health levels — see 'subsystems' diagram for per-component breakdown.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 35
    }
  ],
